Package de.targodan.usb.io

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DataSource
    Implementations of DataSource represent a data source for IRC messages.
    IRCClient
    IRCClient represents a supported IRC client.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CaseManagerFactory
    CaseManagerFactory creates a CaseManager with DataSources as defined in the given Config.
    Config
    Config represents the configuration of the UberSpatchBoard.
    Config.DataSource
    DataSource represents the configuration of a data source.
    DataConsumer
    DataConsumer consumes, parses and handles messages from arbitrarily many DataSources.
    Hexchat
    Hexchat represents the HexChat IRC client.
    IRCClientRegistry
    The IRCClientRegistry keeps track of all supported IRC client types.
    IRCFormatFilteringReader
    Represents a filter for IRC formatting special characters.
    mIRC
    mIRC represents the mIRC IRC client.
    PathSanitizer
    PathSanitizer is a helper to clean up paths and resolve environment variables that may contained in a path.
    ReaderDataSource
    ReaderDataSource is an implementation of DataSource reading Strings from a BufferedReader.
    SingleChannelFileDataSource
    The SingleChannelFileDataSource is a ReaderDataSource that creates a reader from a file.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    OperatingSystem
    OperatingSystem represents the supported operating systems.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    UnsupportedOperatingSystemException
